info.name: ECommerceAPI-Deployed
info.description:
Routes are described per folder, except for folders that describes Authorization.

Ex. Requests contained by the folder of path: `/users/register/` will have a request address of the corresponding directory `http://ec2-3-142-164-9.us-east-2.compute.amazonaws.com/b5/users/register`.

Folders labeled`\*No Token, \*Admin Token`, and `\*Non-Admin Token` are exceptions to this rule.

Requests serves as test-cases to simulate each endpoints known expected outputs.
